#

Creamy Garlic Butter Chicken

$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh Protein

Tags:

EasyPopularComfort Food

Description

A rich and creamy garlic butter sauce envelops tender chicken for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • Chicken breasts: 4 pieces
  • Butter: 4 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Heavy cream: 1 cup
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
